sequenceDiagram
    participant U as 👤 User<br/>Copilot Chat
    participant A as 🤖 Triage Agent<br/>Declarative Agent
    participant S1 as Step 1<br/>EXTRACT
    participant S2 as Step 2<br/>CLASSIFY
    participant S3 as Step 3<br/>RECOMMEND
    participant PB as 📋 Playbook<br/>Registry<br/>(YAML Files)
    participant ADO as 🔧 Azure DevOps<br/>REST API

    U->>A: New work item / bug report
    Note over A: Prompt Chain begins<br/>Each step has its own<br/>system prompt

    A->>S1: Raw input text
    Note over S1: Extract structured fields:<br/>• Title, Description<br/>• Affected component<br/>• Error signatures<br/>• Reproduction steps
    S1->>A: Structured JSON

    A->>S2: Structured fields
    Note over S2: Classify:<br/>• Severity (P0-P4)<br/>• Category (Bug/Feature/Task)<br/>• Team assignment<br/>• SLA tier
    S2->>A: Classification result

    A->>PB: Lookup: category + severity
    PB-->>A: Matching playbook YAML

    A->>S3: Classification + Playbook
    Note over S3: Recommend actions:<br/>• Suggested assignee<br/>• Required fields<br/>• Escalation path<br/>• Related work items
    S3->>A: Action recommendations

    A->>ADO: Update work item<br/>(fields + tags + assignment)
    ADO-->>A: Confirmation

    A->>U: ✅ Triaged: P2 Bug → Team X<br/>Playbook: "database-errors"<br/>Assigned: @engineer
